==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: carjacking
<hw>car"jack*ing</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>car</ets> +
hi<ets>jacking</ets>.]</ety> <def>the forcible taking of a car while the
driver is in it; the robber may force the driver out, force the driver
to drive while under threat of harm, or be forced to relinquish the
controls while also being forced to remain in the car. In the latter two
cases, the act also constitutes a kidnapping.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

